        of Arts Oven
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">Dive into a collection of beautifully crafted components and
        seamless themes that bring your projects to life with style and functionality.</p>

    <div class="window mt-10">
        <div class="tile-bar">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="window-content relative">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 w-full items-start">

                <div>
                    <div class="card w-full">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1643584549066-fc993fc9cb43?q=80&w=3870&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D"/>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="card-title flex items-center gap-2">Hello world! <span class="badge badge-error">New</span>
                            </h2>
                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit.</p>
                            <div class="card-footer justify-end">
                                <button class="btn btn-primary">Add Cart</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-4 items-start mt-6 border border-base-300 p-4 rounded-[var(--border-radius)]">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="gender" class="form-switch"/>
                        <label>Send me updates</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-span-2">
                    <div class="alert alert-outline-success mt-0" role="alert">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M8.37988 12.0001L10.7899 14.4201L15.6199 9.58008" stroke="currentColor"
                                  stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
